      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms mzPeak uses Parquet format with compression, but does NOT describe mzPeak as a 'ZIP archive'. Parquet is a columnar storage format, not a ZIP archive. The output format description in the card appears to conflate Parquet with ZIP compression.",
